Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特典影像
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.80,0:00:12.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊藤静为接近雏菊学习剑道之卷
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.52,0:00:37.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是伊藤静
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.46,0:00:59.83,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}本特典影像是把平日里为「旋风管家」努力的诸位演员\N当成大小姐让Staff管家来满足她们的各种愿望（※预算内）的企划!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.91,0:00:41.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次的特典影像呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.87,0:00:48.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说呢  看我穿成这个样子大家就应该明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.56,0:00:56.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雏菊的剑道很强  那么我也来练习一下剑道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.48,0:01:04.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在很兴奋  这次还请来了老师来教我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.85,0:01:06.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,片野老师
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.04,0:01:16.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天呢  由于你是第一次学习剑道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.02,0:01:19.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这大约一个半小时的时间里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.17,0:01:23.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不知道你大概能学习到什么程度
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.98,0:01:25.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你能尽量学习
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.21,0:01:25.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.75,0:01:28.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后如果能够和人比赛就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.26,0:01:31.33,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}（最终目标是比赛!!）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.48,0:01:29.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.34,0:01:30.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.19,0:01:39.08,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}（其一  竹刀的持法）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.55,0:01:45.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像这样把竹刀放在右手关节的位置  然后这样握住
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.45,0:01:48.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里就是你右手握住的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.49,0:01:48.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.54,0:01:53.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后…这边是向前的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.47,0:01:54.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.70,0:01:56.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后左手的小指
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.33,0:01:57.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小指
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.07,0:01:58.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钩住竹刀的底部
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.57,0:02:00.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  钩住
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.36,0:02:06.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是为了在刺的时候不向前滑动  这样握的话就会滑出去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.22,0:02:05.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.26,0:02:08.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那握刀的时候就要保持钩住的状态
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.23,0:02:11.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来是持刀的姿势
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.71,0:02:13.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左手要贴在肚脐的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.08,0:02:18.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,双臂是弯曲的姿势  这里也会保持放松
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.02,0:02:21.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后  竹刀的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.89,0:02:23.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刀尖的高度和喉咙的高度相比…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.00,0:02:24.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喉咙的高度
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.79,0:02:26.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微低一些
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.32,0:02:26.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.50,0:02:31.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是手的基本姿势
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.65,0:02:32.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.95,0:02:37.87,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}（其二  基本姿势·步法）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.18,0:02:39.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来学习脚的姿势
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.38,0:02:42.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脚呢  就像平时走路时候的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.33,0:02:49.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右脚落地  然后左脚就会抬起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.59,0:02:50.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是刚刚抬起瞬间的动作
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.02,0:02:53.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是持刀的姿势
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.10,0:02:57.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前脚就这样向前
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.26,0:02:57.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向前
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.25,0:03:00.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后左脚脚后跟是抬起的状态
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.95,0:03:06.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个时候  脚后跟是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.33,0:03:08.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果这样斜过去的话身体就是「半身」的姿势了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.33,0:03:08.20,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（半身：剑道中与对手连线稍微倾斜的姿势）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.31,0:03:08.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全是直的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.75,0:03:09.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的两脚的距离有一些宽了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.17,0:03:10.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宽了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.59,0:03:12.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距离稍微缩一些  这样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.20,0:03:13.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边  原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.83,0:03:15.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是距离过近的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.18,0:03:15.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就动不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.71,0:03:17.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  就动不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.25,0:03:17.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的距离就可以了是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.95,0:03:19.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前脚脚尖到后脚脚跟大概一步半
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.90,0:03:22.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,间隔大概是地板的一条左右
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.08,0:03:24.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像这样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.79,0:03:26.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微  稍微向后一点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.45,0:03:27.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的好的好的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.18,0:03:33.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来这样  在这个姿势下听到「前」的时候就向前迈一步
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.75,0:03:35.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迈完这一步之后后脚就贴上来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.71,0:03:36.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  贴上来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.54,0:03:37.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是贴上来…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.49,0:03:38.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  刚才的姿势
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.19,0:03:39.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保持这样的姿势
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.57,0:03:40.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保持这样的姿势跟上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.77,0:03:41.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后还是同样的姿势
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.91,0:03:42.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.67,0:03:45.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后在向前迈步时候  右腿的膝盖
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.56,0:03:47.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右腿的膝盖不要抬起来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.52,0:03:48.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不抬起来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.17,0:03:51.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要绷紧  要绷紧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.63,0:03:54.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么来练习一下前进和后退吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.84,0:03:55.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.39,0:04:01.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  前  前  后  后
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.27,0:04:07.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后  前  前  前
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.67,0:04:12.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后  后  前  前
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.68,0:04:14.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后  后
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.80,0:04:15.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很累是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.97,0:04:20.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微休息一下  活动活动肩膀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.60,0:04:25.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是拿着竹刀就已经…相当辛苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.25,0:04:26.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.63,0:04:34.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看的时候以为就是这么打一打  没想到这么累
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.69,0:04:28.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且很重吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.79,0:04:40.82,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}（其三  面击分解动作）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.55,0:04:43.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面击的分解动作
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.03,0:04:48.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一的时候  保持这样的姿势一直向上抬  左手抬到最高
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.79,0:04:49.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  左手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.13,0:04:50.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左手要抬上去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.93,0:04:51.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抬不上去…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.00,0:04:53.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再往上抬  再往上抬
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.62,0:04:54.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抬不上去～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.63,0:04:55.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再往上抬
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.46,0:04:56.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抬不上去～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.64,0:04:57.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.55,0:04:59.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  一
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.12,0:05:00.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.98,0:05:02.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.88,0:05:03.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.80,0:05:07.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伸直  这里要伸直
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.61,0:05:09.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  三
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.59,0:05:13.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二的时候  二的时候就打到对方的面部了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.28,0:05:16.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以一完了  二的时候要喊「面」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.02,0:05:18.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三  回来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.26,0:05:19.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那稍微练习一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.20,0:05:22.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从基本姿势开始
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.83,0:05:24.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.68,0:05:27.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二  面！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.39,0:05:28.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.36,0:05:31.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三的时候要保持基本姿势
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.29,0:05:32.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  一
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.01,0:05:34.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二  面！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.67,0:05:35.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.20,0:05:36.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.11,0:05:38.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二  面！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.66,0:05:39.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.22,0:05:40.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.02,0:05:42.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二  面！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.56,0:05:43.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.30,0:05:44.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.63,0:05:47.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是完全不知道自己在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.09,0:05:50.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很不错  很不错  但手臂要能伸直就更好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.24,0:05:50.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伸直
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.07,0:05:56.84,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}（其四  面击）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.44,0:06:01.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站在这里的话  「一  二  面」的话是打不到的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.97,0:06:04.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以真正要打的时候要向前跳出去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.67,0:06:07.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像这样大步迈出去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.14,0:06:12.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后刚才我们看到的防具大概有二十公斤重
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.23,0:06:16.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,练习的时候相当的累
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.89,0:06:21.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大约练习两个小时  就能出两公斤左右的汗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.04,0:06:28.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是这样  只是像现在一样空挥就能出那么多的汗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.08,0:06:30.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相当辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.13,0:06:35.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.01,0:06:38.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.89,0:06:40.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.36,0:06:42.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师你也指导我一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.38,0:06:50.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脚好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.04,0:06:52.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.79,0:06:55.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好累
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.28,0:07:01.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.63,0:07:02.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不错  真不错
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.43,0:07:06.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是有点紧了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.35,0:07:07.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紧
