Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.31,0:07:10.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  这里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.12,0:07:12.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些紧  这样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.97,0:07:16.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面！
